此地下車站設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]<ref name="tracks">{{NYCS const|trackref|trackbook3}}</ref>和四條軌道，以及一簾牆分隔慢車和快車軌道<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm18.jpg|title=The low ceiling of the extension at the northern end of the Bay Ridge-bound platform|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|date=October 1, 2012|website=subwaynut.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150602045508/http://subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm18.jpg|archive-date=2015-06-02|dead-url=no|access-date=December 18, 2018}}</ref>。

月台除北端外沒有樑柱。1960年代月台延長至現時標準{{link-en|紐約地鐵B分部|B Division (New York City Subway)|B分部}}列車長度600英呎時加設。這些工字樑柱是奶白色的，天花板亦較低<ref name="#1"/>。2017年翻新時，1970年代安裝的煤渣磚重新裝上，安裝了新的黑色地磚和黃色月台踏板。1970年代安裝的藍色煤渣磚由小型黑色馬賽克磚蓋過<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/mtaphotos/38090305082/in/album-72157665791153429/|title=Reopening of the Prospect Av R Station|last=Cashin|first=Patrick|date=November 2, 2017|website=Flickr|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=December 18, 2018}}</ref>。

此站在2017年的藝術品是由{{link-en|莫尼卡·布拉沃|Monika Bravo}}設計的馬賽克<ref>{{cite web | last=Plitt | first=Amy | title=Brooklyn’s Prospect Ave subway station reopens after six-month revamp | website=Curbed NY | date=November 3, 2017 | url=https://ny.curbed.com/2017/11/3/16601592/mta-nyc-subway-brooklyn-prospect-avenue | access-date=November 4, 2017 | archive-date=2019-08-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821062324/https://ny.curbed.com/2017/11/3/16601592/mta-nyc-subway-brooklyn-prospect-avenue | dead-url=no }}</ref>，顯示了當地的地標如{{link-en|布魯克林軍隊基地|Brooklyn Army Terminal}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.brooklynpaper.com/stories/40/45/dtg-prospect-avenue-station-reopens-2017-11-10-bk.html|title=Back on tracks: Refurbished Prospect Avenue station reopens, delighting local straphangers|last=Mixson|first=Colin|date=November 3, 2017|work=Brooklyn Paper|access-date=November 4, 2017|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821062325/https://www.brooklynpaper.com/stories/40/45/dtg-prospect-avenue-station-reopens-2017-11-10-bk.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 出口 ===
車站唯一的付費區位於近中央部分的月台層<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm20.jpg|title=Approaching the turnstiles to leave the station from the Bay Ridge-bound platform, the waiting area doesn't allow the token clerk to provide a mindful eye anymore, the only token clerk is now on the Manhattan-bound platform|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|date=October 1, 2012|website=subwaynut.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311015816/http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm20.jpg|archive-date=2016-03-11|dead-url=no|access-date=December 18, 2018}}</ref>。直至2017年翻新為止<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/mtaphotos/38067569996/in/album-72157665791153429/|title=Prospect Av Station Reopens|last=Hermann|first=Marc A.|date=November 2, 2017|website=Flickr|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=December 18, 2018}}</ref>，車站設有原初的修剪線、特定距離髤上棕色「P」字、一系列閘機和詢問處<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm8.jpg|title=Looking through the fence to the area outside of fare control at a P in the station's trim at Prospect Avenue.|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|date=June 5, 2009|website=subwaynut.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311015826/http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm8.jpg|archive-date=2016-03-11|dead-url=no|access-date=December 18, 2018}}</ref>。往曼哈頓方向設有兩條樓梯往第四大道近{{link-en|展望高速公路|Prospect Expressway}}以東行人路，而往灣脊區側設有一條樓梯往展望大道和第四大道西南角<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm22.jpg|title=The one streetstair from the Bay Ridge-bound platform|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|date=October 1, 2012|website=subwaynut.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821062329/http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm22.jpg|archive-date=2019-08-21|dead-url=no|access-date=December 18, 2018}}</ref><ref name=MTA-ParkSlopeMap-2015>{{cite web|title=MTA Neighborhood Maps: Park Slope|url=http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/bkn/B3_Park_Slope_2015.pdf|website=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|mta.info]]|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=August 2, 2015|date=2015|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724175624/http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/bkn/B3_Park_Slope_2015.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。車站不設上跨道或下穿道<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm15.jpg|title=The other entrance the Manhattan-bound platform at Prospect Av, with the Expressway as the backdrop.|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|date=June 29, 2009|website=subwaynut.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311013539/http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm15.jpg|archive-date=2016-03-11|dead-url=no|access-date=December 18, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm13.jpg|title=Looking out from the Prospect Expressway's overpass at the single staircase down to the Bensonhurst & Bay Ridge side at Prospect Ave.|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|date=June 29, 2009|website=subwaynut.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015022646/http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/prospectm/prospectm13.jpg|archive-date=2012-10-15|dead-url=no|access-date=December 18, 2018}}</ref>。

